LDK Solar to Issue 3 Billion Yuan of Medium-Term Notes

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-11-30T03:53:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-30/ldk-solar-to-issue-3-billion-yuan-of-medium-term-notes.html
LDK Solar Co. plans to sell 3
billion yuan of medium-term notes, according to a statement on
the Chinese government bond clearing house website today.  The company will initially sell 500 million yuan of three-
year bonds Dec. 7 to repay bank loans, according to the
statement. The remaining amount is scheduled to be sold next
year, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  